STUDENT: So the original
inspiration was from Minecraft.

00:00:33.730 --> 00:00:35.980
And we were kind of
constructing this cubes freely

00:00:35.980 --> 00:00:38.347
with different textures.

00:00:38.347 --> 00:00:39.555
And we made this with Kinect.

00:00:39.555 --> 00:00:41.080
So basically with
one hand you can

00:00:41.080 --> 00:00:45.690
control the position of your
character, which is a ball.

00:00:45.690 --> 00:00:47.740
And with the other
hand, you can decide

00:00:47.740 --> 00:00:50.440
whether to create,
which is going up,

00:00:50.440 --> 00:00:52.590
and eat, which is going down.

00:00:52.590 --> 00:00:56.240
So because now we are
deleting this cubes.

