STUDENT: Always gauge.

00:01:07.290 --> 00:01:11.412
But when you use the
hand out, it will delete.

00:01:11.412 --> 00:01:12.650
[LAUGHTER]

00:01:12.650 --> 00:01:14.574
STUDENT: So it's a little
bit hard to select.

00:01:14.574 --> 00:01:17.460
