randomly located--

00:01:47.510 --> 00:01:48.520
STUDENT: Oh yes.

00:01:48.520 --> 00:01:53.930
At first we had the problem
that, when the cube is created,

00:01:53.930 --> 00:01:55.420
it overlapped each other.

00:01:55.420 --> 00:01:59.300
So then we do make
it at the position

00:01:59.300 --> 00:02:05.090
