cube has side, a unique cube.

00:02:05.090 --> 00:02:08.905
So it will not overlap anymore.

00:02:08.905 --> 00:02:13.130
And in the future, we may
consider group the object.

00:02:13.130 --> 00:02:18.030
So we either go to move the
whole one object together.

00:02:18.030 --> 00:02:21.950
For example, if you have
a house or anything,

00:02:21.950 --> 00:02:23.875
then you can move
it at one time.

